    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with plenty of character? This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for someone who values reliability and is ready to provide a little TLC! It runs and drives well, though it does show its age with some cosmetic wear and a few minor mechanical needs. It's an honest car at a great price, perfect for someone looking for a solid foundation to improve over time!",
